reviewText: The director has a strong love for film and you can see it through his work. Slimy little bastards is a fun horror comedy that shows you don't necessarily need a lot of money to make a movie but a passion for film.
Packaged arrived in a nice timely order and boxed up nicely. No complaints! Everything was wrapped and nice and clean. Thank you so much!
An incredibly fun movie that you could tell was important to everyone who took part in it. Several of the actors got a chance to experiment with unusual characters throughout the vignettes.
This is an entertaining anthology film. Gooey, sticky, and fun as all hell!
